                                                        <p class="s_title">Ultra-slim, ultra-powerful</p>
                                                        <p>Not many laptops offer such a standout blend of style and power as the Samsung ATIV Book 9 2014 Edition. Its seductively
                                                            slim, contoured aluminum body is lightweight and just 0.63 inches (16 millimeters) thick, making it easy to hold and
                                                            carry. It's also built for maximum performance with an Intel Core i5 processor, 8GB of memory, and a 128GB solid state
                                                            drive which combine for speedy and smooth multitasking for everything from demanding work tasks to multimedia
                                                            entertainment.</p>
                                                    </div>
