                                                        <div class="group">
                                                            <div class="item_left">
                                                                <p class="s_title">Vibrant Full HD display</p>
                                                                <p>Whether its movies, videos, photos, or web pages, everything looks crystal clear and lifelike on the ATIV Book
                                                                    9's roomy 15.6-inch (396.24-millimeter) touchscreen display with wide viewing angles.</p>
                                                                <p class="s_title">Ergonomic keyboard and touchpad</p>
                                                                <p>The ATIV Book 9's keyboard features stylish, curved key caps that cushion your fingertips, while the touchpad
                                                                    ensures precision, accuracy, and fast response.</p>
                                                                <p class="s_title">Powerful Intel Core i5 processor</p>
                                                                <p>A fourth-generation Intel Core i5 processor delivers faster system performance, uses less power, and enables
                                                                    sharper graphics.</p>
                                                                <p class="s_title">All-day computing power</p>
                                                                <p>Up to nine hours of battery life* means you'll have plenty of juice for a full day in the office, marathon
                                                                    movie-watching sessions, or even a transatlantic flight.</p>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="item_right"><img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0097/2954/0154/files/d1.jpg?v=1529920091" alt=""></div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="item">
