                                                                <img src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0097/2954/0154/files/d3.jpg?v=1529920148" alt="">
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="item_right">
                                                                <p class="s_title">GPS Running Watch with Multisport Features and Wrist-based Heart Rate</p>
                                                                <ul>
                                                                    <li>A7 chip with 64-bit architecture</li>
